Acer Rises for First Time in Six Days After Chief Executive Lanci Resigns

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-04-01T01:11:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/acer-rises-for-first-time-in-six-days-after-chief-executive-lanci-resigns.html
Acer Inc. (2353)  shares rose for the first
time in six trading days after it yesterday announced Chief
Executive Officer Gianfranco Lanci resigned after clashing with
board members over future strategy.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
